        Alongside DriverWeb, we developed a dedicated <strong>Navigation App</strong>, which integrates seamlessly via deep links. 
        It uses socket communication to send real-time location data to the server and provides turn-by-turn navigation powered by Here Maps.
    </p>
    <p>
        The app constructs the navigation route based on route points received from the server, ensuring accurate and up-to-date driving instructions 
